OL,3,CFlights disrupted across Middle East
OL,4,Cand beyond following Iran strikes
OL,6,FFlights across the Middle East and
OL,7,Fbeyond have been thrown into chaos
OL,8,Fafter airspaces were closed following
OL,9,Fthe US and Israel's attack on Iran.
OL,11,FDubai International Airport - the
OL,12,Fworld's busiest hub for international
OL,13,Fflights - reported more than 700
OL,14,Finbound and outbound cancellations.
OL,16,FThe airport's operator said flights
OL,17,Fwere halted indefinitely at Dubai
OL,18,FInternational and Dubai World Central
OL,19,F- Al Maktoum International Airport on
OL,20,Fthe Gulf city's outskirts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
