OL,3,CFlights disrupted across Middle East
OL,4,Cand beyond following Iran strikes
OL,6,FIsrael, the United Arab Emirates and
OL,7,FQatar closed their airspace on
OL,8,FSaturday.
OL,10,FAirspace in southern Syria was also
OL,11,Fclosed, as were skies above Iran,
OL,12,FIraq, Kuwait and Bahrain and Oman's
OL,13,FMuscat International Airport,
OL,14,Faccording to flight tracking website
OL,15,FFlightRadar24.
OL,17,FPlanes that were en route to cities
OL,18,Flike Tel Aviv and Dubai early on
OL,19,FSaturday were diverted or returned to
OL,20,Fwhere they took off from.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
