OL,3,CFlights disrupted across Middle East
OL,4,Cand beyond following Iran strikes
OL,6,FThe situation is changing quickly and
OL,7,Fairlines urged passengers to check
OL,8,Ftheir flight status online before
OL,9,Fheading to the airport.
OL,11,FSome airlines were issuing waivers to
OL,12,Faffected travellers, meaning fliers
OL,13,Fcan rebook their flight plans without
OL,14,Fpaying extra fees or higher fares.
OL,16,FJonathan Escott and his fiance had
OL,17,Farrived at the airport in Newcastle,
OL,18,FEngland, only to find out that his
OL,19,Fdirect flight to Dubai on Emirates
OL,20,Fairline was cancelled, leaving
OL,21,Feveryone on the flight stuck there.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
