OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772416988
OL,3,CFlights disrupted across Middle East
OL,4,Cand beyond following Iran strikes
OL,6,FEscott left to go back to where he was
OL,7,Fstaying with family, about an hour
OL,8,Ffrom the airport, but has no idea when
OL,9,Fhe may be able to travel.
OL,11,F"No one knows," Escott said. "No one
OL,12,Freally knows what's going on with the
OL,13,Fconflict, really. Not Emirates,
OL,14,FEmirates don't have a clue. No one has
OL,15,Fa clue."
OL,17,FThe airspace closures were likely to
OL,18,Fhave significant ripple effects for
OL,19,FDubai-based Emirates and many other
OL,20,Fairlines that fly in and out of the
OL,21,FMiddle East.
