OL,3,CFlights disrupted across Middle East
OL,4,Cand beyond following Iran strikes
OL,6,FBritish Airways said flights to Tel
OL,7,FAviv and Bahrain will be suspended
OL,8,Funtil next week, and flights to Amman,
OL,9,FJordan, will be cancelled on Saturday.
